comments.body:
In 0f2381ae6058ff12197c9ac0bcacbe380a55b206 "wallet: early error when db directory is not writable"

Nit to highlight it even further that `ec` is unused.
```diff
@@ -321,8 +321,8 @@ bool IsDirWritable(const fs::path& dir_path)

     if (auto created{fsbridge::fopen(tmp, mode)}) {
         std::fclose(created);
-        std::error_code ec;
-        fs::remove(tmp, ec); // clean up, ignore errors
+        std::error_code _;
+        fs::remove(tmp, _); // clean up, ignore errors
         return true;
     }
     return false;
```

